### Send Text with Reply (Quote Message)
# Note: Replace "MESSAGE_ID_HERE" with actual message ID from webhook
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send-text
Authorization: Basic {{username}}:{{password}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session": "{{session}}",
  "to": "{{phoneNumber}}",
  "text": "This is a reply to your message!",
  "quoted_message_id": "AC1BFEE060D325F55FF5CB227BE18973"
}

### Send Image with Reply
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send-image
Authorization: Basic {{username}}:{{password}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session": "{{session}}",
  "to": "{{phoneNumber}}",
  "text": "Here's an image in reply to your message",
